sources.title: Labyrinthus (Multiple award-winning ADVENTURES for the whole family, Adventure Films German 2023)

metadata.Plot: Cool schoolboy Frikke (14) accidentally finds a tries a non-commercialized VR labyrinth video game which allows uploading the player's own pictures of objects and creatures, but finds the original is gravely affected. That applies to an amnesiac airhead girl who can only survive if he guides her to survive and win the game he also discovers as he goes against the evil, experienced challenger and presumed creator 'Pek', by finding a code. Frikke finds out it's Nola, his buddy Marko's would be-flame Isa. It becomes a ream nightmare when Marko is also caught in he game, hence hospitalized comatose, but at least he proves a gifted player and enjoys being Isa's hero. Setting a trap to identify Pek, Frikke bumps into ally player and IT-whiz Rudolf, who reveals the whole conundrum, so they team up.
metadata.Actors: Spencer Bogaert, Emma Verlinden, Felix Maesschalck
